headline: Eaton Declares Quarterly Dividend Payable November 21, 2025
summary: DUBLIN, October 21, 2025--The Board of Directors of intelligent power management company Eaton (NYSE:ETN) today declared a quarterly dividend of $1.04 per ordinary share. The dividend is payable November 21, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on November 6, 2025. Eaton has paid dividends on its shares every year since 1923.
